| 2          | Public key flags           
                       
                       0x01 : internally generated change address. Control rule amount restriction
                       will not apply
                                                                                                    | 1
| 3-4        | CRC-16 of the structure computed after setting current bytes to 0000                 | 2
| 5-10       | Nonce                                                                                | 7
| 11         | Bitcoin address version                                                              | 1
